cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically with image completion and scene reconstruction. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves graphics and visualization, which suggests cs.GR (Computer Graphics) as the second likely category. The use of big data applications and machine learning techniques indicates cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as possible categories. Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method and comparison with existing techniques suggests cs.LG (Machine Learning) as a possible category.
